            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>深圳流感升至“中风险”！这6类人尤其要小心】深圳市疾病风险综合预报结果显示，当前深圳流感的风险等级为“中”。最近一周，全市哨点医院报告的流感个案数有上升趋势，主要由甲型流感病毒引起。根据既往年份监测结果，深圳已开始进入流感活跃期，学校、托幼机构、养老机构等单位应做好流感防控工作，尽可能降低聚集性疫情的发生。到底什么是流感？如何区别甲流和普通感冒？该怎样预防？别急，卫这就来解答👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E9%A2%84%E6%8A%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E9%A2%84%E6%8A%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#疾病风险预报#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qbti5qj20ll0g8tc3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qcuta0j20v96ox4qp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qdl4c1j20v95t6x3i.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qe48ygj20v93k3tnu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qbd4jkj20v94yy1ga.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hby0qafg2bj20p70b8gn9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
