            <description><![CDATA[【罕见！50岁阿姨的子宫肌瘤长进心脏里！14个科室联手摘瘤】5分钟前，50岁的金姐（化名）晕倒了。她双手抖个不停，小便失禁......家人急忙跑过来，却怎么也叫不醒。经医院检查出金姐心脏里有一个大概9cm的肿瘤，而这之后，金姐又晕了2次。她辗转来到深圳市人民医院，心外科主任判断这应该是“侵入心脏静脉内血管平滑肌瘤病”，并建议她找妇科主任，医生顺藤摸瓜，果然在金姐的盆腔右侧，发现了一团直径约5cm的不明肿瘤👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F76Tsdu6F7ORX-PN6tnhQWA" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">罕见！50岁阿姨的子宫肌瘤长进心脏里！14个科室联手摘瘤</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbvstmxip9j20u076mqog.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbvstlquhcj20ma7ps4nt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbvpd5cawzj20u048cwu4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
